Definition: perennial herb of northeastern United States having a thick knotted yellow rootstock and large rounded leaves
Synonyms: golden_seal, yellow_root, turmeric_root, Hydrastis_Canadensis, herbaceous_plant, genus_Hydrastis, m, perennial, herb, of, northeastern, United, States, having, a, thick, knotted, yellow, rootstock, and, large, rounded, leaves
Category: noun.plant
